Class CovariantTypeSemantics

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.microbean.type.TypeSemantics
      • org.microbean.type.CovariantTypeSemantics
  • @Experimental
public final class CovariantTypeSemantics
extends TypeSemantics
    A TypeSemantics specialization that implements the Java Language Specification type assignability rules.

    Laird Nelson
